<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Easter Prayer</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Apr 05, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Prayer for a rainy Easter Day:
</p>

 <p>
The refreshing rain <br></br>
falls upon the parched land <br></br>
And brings life to the <br></br>
cracked, barren earth.
</p>

 <p>
In the same way, may the <br></br>
Spirit of the risen Christ <br></br>
heal our broken hearts and <br></br>
restore our barren souls.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>




